  <entry>
    <title>scratchWeb_1</title>
    <link href="http://unsc1902.github.io/20180201/scratch_1/"/>
    <id>http://unsc1902.github.io/20180201/scratch_1/</id>
    <published>2018-02-01T04:36:43.000Z</published>
    <updated>2018-02-01T08:27:14.768Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<blockquote class="blockquote-center"><p>scratch_web 3.0<br>构建问题及解决方案</p>
</blockquote>
<a id="more"></a>
<h1 id="开源scratch3-0"><a href="#开源scratch3-0" class="headerlink" title="开源scratch3.0"></a>开源scratch3.0</h1><p>开源<a href="https://github.com/LLK/scratch-gui" target="_blank" rel="external">github</a></p>
<h1 id="编译过程"><a href="#编译过程" class="headerlink" title="编译过程"></a>编译过程</h1><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">npm install</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="issues"><a href="#issues" class="headerlink" title="issues"></a>issues</h2><ol>
<li>编译过程中,chromedriver组件由于各种问题无法安装，尝试网上方法更换镜像源失败<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">npm install chromedriver --chromedriver_cdnurl=http://cdn.npm.taobao.org/dist/chromedriver</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
</ol>
<p>解决方案：下载node_chromedriver源码<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">git clone https://github.com/giggio/node-chromedriver.git</div><div class="line">cd node-chromedriver</div><div class="line">npm install</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>安装完依赖包后会进入下载等待状态，此时可中止安装手动下载<br><a href="https://chromedriver.storage.googleapis.com/2.35/chromedriver_linux64.zip" target="_blank" rel="external">Download</a><br>保存到/tmp/chromedriver/chromedriver_linux64.zip后重新<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">node ./install.js</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>即可完成安装</p>
<h1 id="启动"><a href="#启动" class="headerlink" title="启动"></a>启动</h1><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">npm start</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>Then go to <a href="http://localhost:8601/" target="_blank" rel="external">here</a>- the playground outputs the default GUI component</p>
]]></content>
    
